content: Cause she walk like a boss, talk like a boss, manicured nails to set the pedicure off. She's fly effortlessly. And she move like a boss, do what a boss do. She got me thinking about getting involved. That's the kinda girl I need. She got her own thing, that's why I love her. Miss Independent, won't you come and spend a little time?
author: Ne-Yo
